# Math Enrollment
## Analysis of enrollment by semester given year
Load Libraries
```{r}
library(tidyverse)
library(infer)
library(moderndive)
library(Stat2Data)
```

Load data from Stat2Data library
```{r}
data("MathEnrollment")
```
```{r}
ggplot(MathEnrollment, aes(x = AYear, y = Fall)) +
  geom_boxplot(color = "black", fill = "darkgreen")

ggplot(MathEnrollment, aes(x = AYear, y = Spring)) +
  geom_boxplot(color = "black", fill = "darkgreen")
```
